						               													<description>You can learn the principles of sustainability by playing with family and friends. Intelligent fun and lots of green-themed challenges.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Zesty is a game to learn how to save the environment&amp;hellip; one challenge at a time! The funniest way to challenge yourself to change your habits step by step.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Help the Planet with small actions that can be done in an hour, a day, a weekend or even several days.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You and your team draw a Challenge card. You will have up to 1 week to complete the highest number of actions listed on the card and, thanks to ZESTY, you will be able to change your habits and those of those who will play with you.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You will read, think, play, record your team's progress on a very special log.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Challenges are divided into five Thematic Areas: Nature, Consumption, Pollution, Society, Emotions and will allow you to reflect on many different topics related to the well-being of the Planet and its inhabitants.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Zesty is a &amp;quot;slow&amp;quot; game: your skills are not demonstrated with speed but with commitment and attention to important topics, which you can explore in a very special book.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Warning: this is a cooperative game. You win, or lose, all together!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
